nning / package selection. <br>10. The execution of the website depends on the difficulty given. <br>11. For communication to us, it\'s on the contact us page. <br>12. DIW is not responsible for any problems that may arise in the future between visitors and the website voters. <br>13. All cheap website packages that we offer include the cost of domain rental and hosting for the first 1 year. <br>14. Domain renewal and hosting fees will notify us via social media or email. <br>15. Website that is ready and ready online, if there are errors or file errors due to editing without notifying us, DIW is not responsible for that error. <br>16. If your website is suspended for violating the law, the constitution, or intellectual property rights (IPR), DIW is not fully responsible. <br>17. Websites that contain such as web gambling, MLM, or soccer betting, we can still make it, provided that DIW is not responsible for that website and if it is violated, we will not deal with legal channels. If your website is deleted, DIW is not responsible, pay attention to the risks. <br>18. Domain extension and hosting fees outside us (except the packages that have been provided) <br>19. DIW does not interfere with the business processes of the company, or the admin panel. <br>20. If the Website has reached the 50% processing time, the payment period will begin within 7 days. If you pass that, DIW will delete all files and the website will be disabled. <br><br>THE RULES AND CONDITIONS OF THESE CONDITIONS ARE ABSOLUTE AND CANNOT BE DISTURBED. <br>WITH YOU BUYING DIW SERVICES OR MAKING A WEBSITE AT US, YOU BEART TO AGREE TO OUR TERMS AND CONDITIONS.', '1. Begitu website anda sudah jadi, kami tidak akan meninggalkan begitu saja, kami tetap memfollow up website anda, seperti bug atau error (dari website yang sudah jadi), dan sebagainya hingga jadi normal. Jadi anda tidak perlu khawatir.<br>2. Kami akan merevisi/memperbaiki permintaan anda secara GRATIS dengan syarat dan ketentuan berlaku (sebe